This supplementary material is distributed solely for the purpose of
reviewing the accompanying NeurIPS 2026 submission "Compressed-Domain
Attention: Tensor-Core Decode for 4-Bit Codebook KV Caches".

Reviewers, area chairs, and program committee members may use the
contents of this archive to verify the claims of the paper. No other
use, redistribution, or derivative work is permitted prior to the
public release of the work by its authors.

The pure-PyTorch reference implementation under cda/algorithm/ is
provided for inspection only and is not licensed for production use.
The result data under results/ is provided as evidence of the reported
measurements and is not licensed for republication.

After the official paper release, the authors intend to release the
production codebase under a permissive open-source license. Until that
release, no rights are granted beyond review-time inspection.
